name: AddressRegistry
description: AddressRegistry. This stores all contract addresses.

eventDecorators.name: OwnershipTransferred
eventDecorators.description: Emitted when a new Vault is deployed.

eventDecorators.name: RegisterNFT
eventDecorators.description: Emitted when a new Vault is deployed. Fired in registerNFT().

eventDecorators.name: UnregisterNFT
eventDecorators.description: Emitted when a new Vault is deployed. Fired in unregisterNFT().

eventDecorators.name: UpdateMarktplace
eventDecorators.description: Emitted when a new Vault is deployed. Fired in updateMarketplace().

eventDecorators.name: UpdateTokenRegistry
eventDecorators.description: Emitted when a new Vault is deployed. Fired in updateTokenRegistry().

functionDecorators.name: owner
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: registerNFT
functionDecorators.description: Register NFT contract addres. Only registered NFT contracts are valid.

functionDecorators.name: renounceOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

functionDecorators.name: transferOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: unregisterNFT
functionDecorators.description: Unregister NFT contract address. Unregistered NFT contracts are invalid.
